    <title>Calc is not accessible to screen readers if sheet is modified [a11y]</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">Hi</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">Steps to reproduce :</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.2">- Activate a screen reader</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.3">- Create a new calc document</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.4">- Navigate on the sheet with keyboard =&gt; Ok it works, coordonates are speaked</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.5">- Modify the current sheet</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.6">- Navigate =&gt; Doesn't work anymore, screen reader doesn't talk anymore about coordonates and contents</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.7">- Delete modified cell =&gt; No sound, can't have sound on this sheet anymore</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.8">- Go to another sheet =&gt; works</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
